      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 20:05:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰森食品上调盈利预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/tyson-raises-profit-outlook-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰森食品公司 (Tyson Foods Inc.) 的季度收益甚至超过了分析师的最高预期，因为鸡肉利润的增加帮助抵消了牛肉业务的损失，促使该公司上调了 2025 年的利润预期。彭博情报的 Jennifer Bartashus 对此进行了报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/tyson-raises-profit-outlook-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 19:58:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贸易战促使市场预期加拿大将进一步降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trade-fight-prompts-markets-to-price-deeper-canada-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于加拿大经济面临与美国长期贸易争端的前景，并可能导致经济衰退，市场开始预期加拿大央行将进一步降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trade-fight-prompts-markets-to-price-deeper-canada-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 19:57:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>五角大楼协助推动移民政策，赫格塞斯访问南部边境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/hegseth-visits-southern-border-as-pentagon-aids-immigration-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国防部长皮特·赫格塞斯前往美国与墨西哥的边境，这是他担任五角大楼负责人后的首次出访，他强调自己愿意让军方参与驱逐出境和移民执法工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/hegseth-visits-southern-border-as-pentagon-aids-immigration-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 19:52:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
